{title: 主你是我力量}
{title_pinyin: Zhǔ nǐ shì wǒ lì liàng}
{key: C}
{tempo: 80}
{language: zh}

{start_of_verse: 主歌/Couplet}
主祢是我力量   zhǔ mí shì wǒ lì liáng
E•n=g8l0is宣hT告ra地nsl、at敬ion拜:J地effNelson,KevinCheng詞、曲：曾祥怡   E n g l is xuān hT gào ra dì nsl at jìng ion bài J dì effNelson KevinCheng cí qǔ céng xiáng yí
